    "body" : "<p>There is a static constant that <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/api/java/math/BigDecimal.html#ZERO\" rel=\"nofollow\">represents 0</a>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>BigDecimal.ZERO.equals(selectPrice)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You should do this instead of:</p>\n\n<pre><code>selectPrice.equals(BigDecimal.ZERO)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>in order to avoid the case where <code>selectPrice</code> is <code>null</code>.</p>\n"
