      "body" : "@nhahtdh Thanks for the information, in fact though there are situations where <code>equals</code> <i>should</i> be used instead of <code>compareTo()</code>. The OP doesn&#39;t specify what type of mathematics he is using, so you&#39;re right it is better to give him both option."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
