    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just want to share here some helpful extensions for kotlin</p>\n\n<pre><code>fun BigDecimal.isZero() = compareTo(BigDecimal.ZERO) == 0\nfun BigDecimal.isOne() = compareTo(BigDecimal.ONE) == 0\nfun BigDecimal.isTen() = compareTo(BigDecimal.TEN) == 0\n</code></pre>\n"
